    "title": "Tohara",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "tohara",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Tamaduni nyingi za kale zilifanya tohara kwa kuondoa govi la kiume (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:25-Jer9:26\">Yeremia 9:25–26</a>).</p><p>Mungu alichagua tohara kama ishara ya agano (makubaliano maalum) inayolenga kizazi. Mungu aliahidi kumfanya Abrahamu na kizazi chake kuwa taifa kubwa na kuwatumia kuwakomboa mataifa yasiyo ya Kiyahudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:2\">Mwanzo 12:2, </a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:3\">3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:3-Gen17:6\">17:3–6</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:8-Gal3:9\">Wagalatia 3:8–9</a>). Tohara ilikuwa alama ya Mungu kwenye mwili. Iliwatambulisha Abrahamu na kizazi chake kama watu wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:9-Gen17:14\">Mwanzo 17:9–14</a>). Iliwakumbusha kuishi kwa uaminifu kwa agano.</p><p>Walifanya tohara kwa wanaume wazima walipojiunga na jamii ya agano (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:23-Gen17:27\">Mwanzo 17:23–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:48\">Kutoka 12:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:3-Josh5:7\">Yoshua 5:3–7</a>). Hata hivyo, kwa kawaida ilifanywa kwa watoto wachanga (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:4\">Mwanzo 21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev12:3\">Mambo ya Walawi 12:3</a>). Watoto wachanga walipokea ahadi za Mungu na kujiunga na jamii ya agano kupitia wazazi wao.</p><p>Imani ilikuwa muhimu ili kupokea baraka za Mungu. Hii ilionyeshwa na tofauti kati ya Ishmaeli na Isaka, Esau na Yakobo, na Yosefu na ndugu zake. Watu wasio Waisraeli pia wangeweza kujiunga na agano la Israeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:48\">Kutoka 12:48</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:15-Gen34:24\">Mwanzo 34:15–24</a>). Tohara ilionyesha kuingizwa kwao katika jamii ya waabudu (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:44\">Kutoka 12:44</a>).</p><p>Tohara iliwasaidia Waisraeli kukumbuka kuweka kando uchafu wa asili. Watu wa Mungu walitakiwa kubaki waaminifu kwa agano, familia zao, na ndoa zao. Kuoa watu wasiotahiriwa nje ya agano kulikuwa ni kuvunja agano. Watu walimfukuza (<em>&quot;cut off&quot;</em>) mtu yeyote aliyekataa tohara (kukata kimwili kwa mfano) kutoka kwa watu wa agano kwa kutotii amri ya Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:14\">Mwanzo 17:14</a>).</p><p>Tohara inaashiria kujitenga na ulimwengu, usafi, na uaminifu kwa agano. Inatoa sitiari yenye nguvu kwa &quot;tohara ya moyo.&quot; Hii inahusu moyo uliojitolea kwa Mungu na kutengwa kwa ajili yake, badala ya kuwa mkaidi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:41\">Mambo ya Walawi 26:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:6\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 30:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:4\">Yeremia 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:26\">9:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:11\">Waefeso 2:11</a>). Tohara ya moyo inaonyesha wokovu na ushirika na Mungu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:31-Ezek18:32\">Ezekieli 18:31–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:25-Ezek36:27\">36:25–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:28-Rom2:29\">Warumi 2:28–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:11\">4:11</a>).</p><p>Wakati Yesu Kristo alipoanzisha agano jipya la Mungu, alitimiza mahitaji ya agano la zamani. Wakristo wa Mataifa hawahitaji tohara kwa sababu imani kwa Yesu inawafanya kuwa sehemu ya watu wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:1-Acts15:29\">Matendo 15:1–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:25-Rom2:29\">Warumi 2:25–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:1-Gal2:10\">Wagalatia 2:1–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:15\">6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:11-Col2:12\">Wakolosai 2:11–12</a>). Mtu lazima amwamini Mungu na ahadi zake, aache matendo ya dhambi na desturi za kidunia, na aishi maisha mapya kwa imani (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33-Jer31:34\">Yeremia 31:33–34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:1-Rom8:17\">Warumi 8:1–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16-Gal6:10\">Wagalatia 5:16–6:10</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:9-Gen17:14\">Mwanzo 17:9–14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:23-Gen17:27\">23–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:4\">21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:1-Gen34:26\">34:1–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:24-Exod4:26\">Kutoka 4:24–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:48\">12:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev12:3\">Mambo ya Walawi 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:2-Josh5:8\">Yoshua 5:2–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:25-Jer9:26\">Yeremia 9:25–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:7-Ezek44:9\">Ezekieli 44:7–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:59\">Luka 1:59</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:21\">2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:1-Acts15:31\">Matendo 15:1–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:1-Acts16:5\">16:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:25-Rom2:29\">Warumi 2:25–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:17-1Cor7:19\">1 Wakorintho 7:17–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:1-Gal5:6\">Wagalatia 5:1–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:11-Gal5:12\">11–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:12-Gal6:16\">6:12–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:11-Eph2:18\">Waefeso 2:11–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:2-Phil3:7\">Wafilipi 3:2–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:11\">Wakolosai 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:11\">3:11</a></p>",
